<br>
<br>
Make toolboxes until they are trivial<br>
Make Skewers until they are trivial<br>
Then you should be able to start making banded armor, start with bracer (usually the easiest to make) and finish off with cloak (usually the hardest to make) after the cloak goes trivial at 175 you should be able to start with FS bracers (made one on my first attempt, and with the stuff I had made 3 outta 4).<br>
<br>
